rows.label: qst701306_msg0001
rows.name:
I know his thick-headedness
well. After all, we've known
each other for a long time.

rows.label: qst701306_msg0002
rows.name:
He wouldn't die even if a woman
stabbed him. He's that kind of man.

rows.label: qst701306_msg0003
rows.name:
But this time, I have a
bad feeling. I don't think
it's possible, but...

rows.label: qst701306_msg0102
rows.name:
Just by looking at your faces,
I can tell it's not good news.
What did that fool do?

rows.label: qst701306_msg0103
rows.name:
Did an old flame find him? Or did he
get involved with someone else's
woman? Did he fall for a honey trap?

rows.label: qst701306_msg0104
rows.name:
With him, it's not possible
that he's dead... right?
